---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.jawaharprasad.com/leadership" />

    <title>How I lead · Jawahar Prasad</title>
    <meta name="description" content="How Jawahar Prasad leads engineering teams: trust through transparency, bias for action, real delegation, and treating everything as learning." />

    <!-- Open Graph (LinkedIn / Twitter sharing) -->
    <meta property="og:type" content="profile" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.jawaharprasad.com/leadership" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="How I lead · Jawahar Prasad" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Trust through transparency, bias for action, real delegation, and treating everything as learning." />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://www.jawaharprasad.com/jawahar.jpg" />

    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="How I lead · Jawahar Prasad" />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Trust through transparency, bias for action, real delegation, and treating everything as learning." />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://www.jawaharprasad.com/jawahar.jpg" />

    <!-- Favicon: minimal text-based via SVG (no separate file needed) -->
    <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 100 100'%3E%3Ctext y='80' font-size='90' font-family='system-ui,sans-serif' font-weight='700'%3EJ%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E" />
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white text-slate-900 antialiased">
    <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">

      <nav class="mb-12">
        <a href="/" class="text-sm text-slate-500 underline decoration-slate-300 hover:decoration-slate-900 underline-offset-4 transition">&larr; Jawahar Prasad</a>
      </nav>

      <header class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">How I lead</h1>
        <p class="mt-1 text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-600">
          The short version, so you know what to expect before we start working together.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section aria-labelledby="lead-by" class="mb-12">
        <h2 id="lead-by" class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-4">In practice</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-800">
          <li>I earn trust by being transparent and by delivering what I said I would.</li>
          <li>I decide fast and act. Most decisions are reversible, and a wrong call you can fix beats a right call made too late.</li>
          <li>I delegate real authority, then trust, verify, and critique the decision without criticizing the person. Once I delegate, I don't micromanage.</li>
          <li>I coach in the moment on what could have been better, and I say so plainly when something was done well.</li>
          <li>I keep the room collaborative and informal. Doing serious work and not taking ourselves too seriously are not in tension.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="value" class="mb-12">
        <h2 id="value" class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-4">What I value</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-800">
          <li><strong>Honesty.</strong> Tell the truth, early and accurately. I'll do the same.</li>
          <li><strong>Transparency.</strong> Openness in good times and bad.</li>
          <li><strong>Energy.</strong> Meeting hard problems with real interest rather than dread.</li>
          <li><strong>Humility.</strong> I'm learning every day, from what works and what doesn't. It's all learning.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="expect" class="mb-16">
        <h2 id="expect" class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-4">What I expect</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-800">
          <li><strong>Reliability.</strong> Do what you said, by when you said. Consistency compounds.</li>
          <li><strong>Speak up.</strong> Say the honest thing clearly, and make room for others to do the same.</li>
          <li><strong>Ownership.</strong> You don't say "that's not my job." You go and get it done.</li>
          <li><strong>Initiative.</strong> Don't wait to be told, and don't need to be followed up with.</li>
          <li><strong>Feedback.</strong> I'm error-prone like everyone. Tell me when I'm wrong.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="more" class="mb-16">
        <h2 id="more" class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-4">More</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg">
          <li>
            <a href="/about" class="text-slate-900 underline decoration-slate-300 hover:decoration-slate-900 underline-offset-4 transition">More about me &rarr;</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jawaharprasad" class="text-slate-900 underline decoration-slate-300 hover:decoration-slate-900 underline-offset-4 transition" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <footer class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 text-sm text-slate-500">
        © Jawahar Prasad · jawaharprasad.com
      </footer>

    </main>
  </body>
</html>
